meta {
  name: 02 Patient data (deterministic)
  seq: 2
}

docs {
  Deterministic reads over the stored fact bundle — **no LLM anywhere in
  this folder**. The panel's landing page renders entirely from these
  endpoints, which is the core architectural claim: patient-safety-relevant
  output (risk flags, contradictions, imaging analysis) comes from pure
  engines over verified EHR facts, not from a model.
}
